4	Veteran Homelessness Facts | Green Doors	How many veterans are homeless? While only 8% of Americans can claim veteran status, 17% of our homeless population is made up of veterans. In 2010, the Department of Veteran Affairs (VA) estimated that on any given night there were 76,000 homeless veterans sleeping on American streets.	http://www.greendoors.org/facts/veteran-homelessness.php
